<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Virtual Production & VR Streaming Masterclass</title>
    <!-- Premium Google Fonts for clean typography -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        /* --- DESIGN SYSTEM (Dark Grey & Bluish-Green) --- */
        :root {
            --bg-main: #0f1115;       /* Deep dark grey background */
            --bg-card: #161a22;       /* Slightly lighter dark grey for containers */
            --text-main: #e2e8f0;     /* Crisp off-white text */
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;    /* Muted grey for descriptions */
            --accent: #00f2fe;        /* Vibrant bluish-green / cyan glow */
            --accent-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b4d8, #00f2fe);
            --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-main);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Centered, narrow content column inspired by Aurelius Tjin's layout */
        .container {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* --- TYPOGRAPHY & HEADINGS --- */
        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        /* Glowing bluish-green text highlight */
        .highlight {
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        p.subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #2e3748, transparent);
            margin: 48px 0;
        }

        /* --- INLINE VR GRAPHICS (SVG) --- */
        .graphic-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .vr-svg {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            stroke: var(--accent);
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 1.5;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.3));
        }

        /* --- VIDEO PLAYER CONTAINER --- */
        .video-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
            height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #000;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #2e3748;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .video-wrapper iframe, 
        .video-wrapper video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 0;
        }

        /* --- FEATURE/TECHNICAL CARDS --- */
        .card {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid #222936;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .card-tag {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.2);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.05);
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* --- CALL TO ACTION BUTTON --- */
        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 48px 0;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-gradient);
            color: #0f1115;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.25);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.4);
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 80px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Custom VR Headset SVG Graphic -->
        <div class="graphic-container">
            <svg class="vr-svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M4 6h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-3.5a2 2 0 0 0-1.5.67L13.67 18a2 2 0 0 1-3.34 0L9 16.67a2 2 0 0 0-1.5-.67H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z"/>
                <circle cx="7" cy="11" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
                <circle cx="17" cy="11" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
                <path d="M12 6v3"/>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Typography Header -->
        <header>
            <h1>The Blueprint For <span class="highlight">Next-Gen VR Streaming</span> & Recording</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">A minimalist guide to capturing zero-lag, ultra-high bitrate virtual production workflows.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Long Form Copy Section -->
        <main>
            <p>Virtual production and immersive 360-degree environments are changing the landscape of digital media. However, capturing high-fidelity VR content presents unique technical hurdles that traditional broadcast systems were never built to handle.</p>
            
            <p>From severe bitrate throttling on standard platforms to spatial audio tracking misalignment, creators constantly face glitches that break immersion. To truly scale a virtual production pipeline, you must optimize your hardware constraints, master hardware-level encoding pipelines, and structure your network for low-latency transmission.</p>

            <hr>

            <h2>Core Technical Pillars</h2>
            <p>Achieving standard-setting playback quality requires separating your workflow into three isolated infrastructure layers:</p>

            <!-- Feature Card 1 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3><span class="card-tag">Layer 01</span> Spatial Encoding</h3>
                <p>Learn how to optimize spatial pixel distribution and render high-density projection matrices without overloading consumer-grade GPU architectures.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature Card 2 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3><span class="card-tag">Layer 02</span> Bitrate Management</h3>
                <p>Configure dedicated local NDI pathways and customized constant-bitrate presets to completely eradicate micro-stuttering and dropped frames during live recordings.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature Card 3 -->
            <div class="card">
                <h3><span class="card-tag">Layer 03</span> Real-time Rendering</h3>
                <p>Synchronize external tracking hardware directly with unreal engines to minimize camera-to-render motion latency down to sub-millisecond ranges.</p>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <!-- Video Section -->
            <h2>A Look Inside the Workflow</h2>
            <p>Watch the breakdown below to see exactly how these modular layers communicate in a live virtual studio environment.</p>
            
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <!-- Replace the src below with your YouTube embed link or your anonymous Dropbox raw link -->
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/g71pjSCFyAU?rel=0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>

            <p>This systematic workflow removes the traditional guesswork out of high-end VR streaming, giving you a repeatable setup that runs flawlessly every single session.</p>

            <!-- Call to Action -->
            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="#" class="cta-btn">Access the Full Architecture File</a>
            </div>

        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>Distributed Anonymously • Pure Content Infrastructure</p>
        </footer>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
